DAT instructions
Follow standalone viewer install instrucitons here if you haven't already:
https://github.com/CCALI/A2JViewer

Make sure you have npm 3.8.x and Node version 5.x installed

1) clone CAJA repo https://github.com/CCALI/CAJA.git
2) `cd` to the CAJA directory
3) `npm install`
4) `cd js`
5) `npm install bootstrap`
6) `cd` back to CAJA directory, `cd ..`
6) change `src/util/paths.js` line 20/getViewerPath function to:

  ```getViewerPath() {
    return path.join(__dirname, '..', '..', '../a2j-viewer/viewer');
  },```

  this assumes stand alone viewer root folder is `a2j-viewer` and at
  the same web root folder as the CAJA directory.

7) `npm run build`
8) `npm run build:server`
9) `npm start`

default Node port is 3000, but can be updated in `bin/www` or overwritten by setting
`process.env.PORT` to the desired port.
